53.3 percent in favor of a tentative four-year labor contract
with  Ford Motor Co. (F) , Local 862 President Todd Dunn said in an
interview.  The local union represents UAW members at two Louisville,
Kentucky, vehicle-assembly plants. The UAWâ€™s Ford department
said earlier today on its Facebook page that 63.2 percent of its
